# Local drafts — kept on disk, untracked, hidden from the public site
# via the `draft: true` frontmatter flag (see src/lib/content.ts
# getAllPosts / getPostBySlug). 2026-07-12.
content/posts/2024-03-17-ia-no-significa-nada.md

# Resume PDF snapshots — generated at build time from local LaTeX repo
# (mirrored by scripts/generate-pdf-snapshots.ts). Never committed.
public/resumes/
# nav-redesign Phase B (2026-07-12): src/data/resumes/*.json are
# build-regenerated artefacts from scripts/generate-json-resume.ts
# (LaTeX → JSON Resume). Tracking them creates noisy diffs and
# fights the pipeline. They are regenerated by `npm run
# generate:resumes` (called from `npm run build:resume-assets`).
src/data/resumes/*.json
# nav-redesign Phase F: public/search-index.json is the ⌘K palette
# data source, generated by `npm run build:search-index` from
# scripts/build-search-index.ts. Tracked nowhere; fresh clones run
# the script during `npm run build`.
public/search-index.json

# private-portfolio-candidates Phase B (2026-07-12):
# `npm run scan:portfolio` produces a per-repo candidate report
# (visibility + include flag + tier + summary + tags). Gitignored
# because it's regenerated on every scan; the source of truth is
# each repo's portfolio.md + portfolio-decisions.json.
portfolio-candidates.md
portfolio-manifests-to-seed/
portfolio-bodies/
